<h2 local-id=3D"db2def50d4a5" id=3D"Task16-TechnicalDocument-3.3Application=
Architecture&amp;UserRequestFlow">3.3 Application Architecture &amp; User R=
equest Flow</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6e1cb25936d5">User Request Flow: The user makes an HTTP requ=
est to the ALB DNS name. The ALB listener on port 80 evaluates routing rule=
s and forwards the request to one of the two healthy EC2 targets in the tas=
k-16-targets target group on port 5000. The Flask application processes the=
 request, queries or writes to MongoDB Atlas via PyMongo using a TLS-encryp=
ted connection string, and returns the response through the ALB back to the=
 user.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrap=
per confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-imag=
e image-center" alt=3D"image (10)-20260322-121651.png" width=3D"468" loadin=
g=3D"lazy" src=3D"b7fd78a61e5622104f42a03aa71294035f8b2323fe10ced6afbe74a27=
1af1d0d" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attac=
hments/1852145714/image%20(10)-20260322-121651.png?version=3D1&amp;modifica=
tionDate=3D1774181873995&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"=
1507" data-width=3D"2209" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-r=
esource-id=3D"1887043829" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-re=
source-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image (10)=
-20260322-121651.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" d=
ata-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-contain=
er-id=3D"1852145714" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-medi=
a-id=3D"428c30bf-19ca-475b-985e-830a821ed508" data-media-type=3D"file" heig=
ht=3D"319"></span>
