</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"ca7630b5c150"><strong>Cost Optimisation Recommendations:</st=
rong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f6d6acfef498">
<li local-id=3D"b1db25af0ff7">
<p local-id=3D"2c467abfc2b6"><strong>Reserved Instances:</strong> Convertin=
g EC2 to 1-year Reserved Instances reduces compute cost by ~40% =E2=80=94 s=
aving ~$7/month per instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7445bef618bd">
<p local-id=3D"47316f8ad34c"><strong>MongoDB Atlas:</strong> M0 free tier i=
s suitable for development and low-traffic production =E2=80=94 upgrade to =
M10 ($57/month) only when data storage or connection requirements exceed fr=
ee tier limits</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"461f628977d9">
<p local-id=3D"c5a1f1c93013"><strong>SSM vs Bastion Host:</strong> Eliminat=
ing a Bastion Host EC2 (typically t3.micro ~$8.47/month) saves cost while i=
mproving security</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e17cdfa1a516">
<p local-id=3D"3baccef0bee3"><strong>Auto Scaling:</strong> Future addition=
 of Auto Scaling Group (ASG) behind ALB enables scale-to-zero during off-pe=
ak hours, reducing EC2 costs</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d1f6a188e13d"><strong>Business Value Analysis:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"65c816406e75">
<li local-id=3D"f5ce5b84e9db">
<p local-id=3D"f93a6b382867"><strong>Deployment Time Reduction:</strong> Ma=
nual SSH-based deployments take 15=E2=80=9320 minutes per instance; SSM Run=
 Command across both instances takes under 2 minutes =E2=80=94 saving 28+ m=
inutes per deployment cycle</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21785faf8d9a">
<p local-id=3D"4139400eaa2c"><strong>Downtime Reduction:</strong> Multi-AZ =
ALB architecture reduces single-node failure impact from 100% downtime to 0=
% (automatic failover to healthy AZ)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3dfb11d63a5d">
<p local-id=3D"4689b0167f13"><strong>Operational Cost:</strong> Managed Mon=
goDB Atlas eliminates DBA overhead for backups, patching, and replication m=
anagement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"91d84df912ab">
<p local-id=3D"aabbf4e5b6d0"><strong>Developer Velocity:</strong> Self-serv=
ice deployments via SSM (without SSH access) reduce DevOps dependency and a=
ccelerate release frequency</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"199d01c03bf2">
