nd the aws:runShellScript action. The deployment steps include: redirecting=
 output to /var/log/deploy.log, changing to the /home/ubuntu directory, clo=
ning or refreshing the FlaskWithMongoDB repository from GitHub, running pip=
3 install -r requirements.txt --break-system-packages, executing systemctl =
restart flaskapp, verifying service status with systemctl status flaskapp -=
-no-pager, and echoing 'Deployment Successful'. This document is the single=
 source of truth for all deployments.</em></p><span class=3D"confluence-emb=
